## Chalk Native Apps (dev only)
## Copy to `apps/native/.env` (gitignored) and fill values.
##
## SECURITY: Do not ship `CHALK_API_KEY` in production mobile apps.
## For production, your backend should mint per-user access tokens.

# Base HTTP API (no trailing slash)
CHALK_API_URL=https://chalk-api.q9labs.ai

# WebSocket URL (must include /ws)
CHALK_WS_URL=wss://chalk-api.q9labs.ai/ws

# Tenant API key (dev only)
CHALK_API_KEY=changeme

# Optional prefix for auto-generated rooms
CHALK_ROOM_PREFIX=native

